<doc id="215253" wikidata="Q1768608" url="?curid=215253" title="Quasi-delict">
<text>Quasi-delict is a French legal term used in some civil law jurisdictions, encompassing the common law concept of &quot;negligence&quot; as the breach of a non-wilful extra-contractual obligation to third parties.

